snippet.title: ANCESTORS: The Humankind Odyssey Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the official announcement trailer for Ancestors: The Humankind Odyssey presented at The Game Awards 2018.
Ancestors: The Humankind Odyssey is a third-person open world survival game from Panache Digital Games published by Private Division. 
Ancestors: The Humankind Odyssey is out now on PC*, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One.
More info on https://www.ancestorsgame.com


*Ancestors: The Humankind Odyssey is available on PC exclusively through the Epic Games Store for the first year, at which point it will come to additional digital PC retailers.
